    <item>
      <title>据称，在与 Diddy 的合作结束后，帝亚吉欧将考虑出售 Ciroc 伏特加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/diageo-is-said-to-weigh-ciroc-vodka-sale-after-diddy-tie-up-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国烈酒集团帝亚吉欧 (Diageo Plc) 正在考虑出售诗珞蔻伏特加 (Cîroc Vodka)，该品牌曾得到音乐大亨肖恩“吹牛老爹”康布斯 (Sean “Diddy” Combs) 的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/diageo-is-said-to-weigh-ciroc-vodka-sale-after-diddy-tie-up-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:33:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行贝利：利率路径“向下”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/boe-s-bailey-path-of-interest-rates-is-downwards-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利讨论了利率、通胀和英国近期经济数据的前景。在货币政策委员会以 6 比 3 的投票结果维持利率不变之后，他发表了讲话，其中三名官员寻求立即降息。（来源：Pool）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/boe-s-bailey-path-of-interest-rates-is-downwards-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:29:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥本海默的斯托尔茨福斯称市场不信任美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/market-doesn-t-trust-fed-oppenheimer-s-stoltzfus-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Oppenheimer 首席投资策略师 John Stoltzfus 表示，他仍然相信股市涨势会扩大，预计不会出现回调。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-19/market-doesn-t-trust-fed-oppenheimer-s-stoltzfus-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:16:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德减记旗舰再生能源基金并改组领导层</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/blackrock-writes-down-flagship-renewable-fund-overhauls-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 表示，在其旗舰可再生基金之一的两项关键投资失败后，该公司正在减记该基金的价值，并正在招募其最近收购的全球基础设施合作伙伴业务的高管来帮助扭转业绩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/blackrock-writes-down-flagship-renewable-fund-overhauls-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:15:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票交易创 23 年来新低，加拿大人应勇于承担风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/canadians-urged-to-take-risks-as-equity-deals-hit-23-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加拿大的交易量已降至 23 年来的最低水平，投资银行家们正在敦促多伦多上市公司收购企业或筹集资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/canadians-urged-to-take-risks-as-equity-deals-hit-23-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 15:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果神秘疾病是多种致命疾病的混合体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/mystery-disease-x-in-congo-is-mix-of-illnesses-that-s-turned-deadly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一种类似流感的疾病导致刚果民主共和国数百人患病，它是该地区常见的多种疾病的混合体，在因饥饿而虚弱的人群中，这些疾病已经演变成严重的疾病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/mystery-disease-x-in-congo-is-mix-of-illnesses-that-s-turned-deadly</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 13:38:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
